<HL>
   Who's News:
   P&amp;G Sets Up Six Units,
   Names 39 New Officers
</HL>
<DATE>
07/11/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B5
</SO>
<CO>
   PG WNEWS
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER NON-CYCLICAL (NCY)
</MS>
